OL,3,CThe hunt for the 'heavy bag man'
OL,4,Cmurderer
OL,6,FIn March 2024, Marcin Majerkiewicz was
OL,7,Fin the midst of trying to get away
OL,8,Fwith murder.
OL,10,FHis victim, 67-year-old Stuart
OL,11,FEverett, had been bludgeoned to death
OL,12,Faround three weeks before with what
OL,13,Fpolice believe was a hammer.
