OL,3,CThe hunt for the 'heavy bag man'
OL,4,Cmurderer
OL,6,FThe murder - which took place in the
OL,7,Fhouse they both shared - had to have
OL,8,Fbeen planned because Marcin
OL,9,FMajerkiewicz had too many tools at his
OL,10,Ffingertips - and almost immediately
OL,11,Fafterwards, he started to chop up
OL,12,FStuart's body parts using a hacksaw,
OL,13,Fbefore casually dumping them across
OL,14,FGreater Manchester.
OL,16,FThe remains were scattered far and
OL,17,Fwide in the hope that nature would
OL,18,Ftake its course and it would be
OL,19,Fdifficult to identify them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
