OL,3,CThe hunt for the 'heavy bag man'
OL,4,Cmurderer
OL,6,FTherefore, if they could just identify
OL,7,Fthat person, well then they'd have
OL,8,Ftheir suspect.
OL,10,FThe hunt for the "heavy bag man" - as
OL,11,Fhe became known - is one of the most
OL,12,Fcomplex cases Greater Manchester
OL,13,FPolice has dealt with in recent years
OL,14,F- and in the latest episode of From
OL,15,FThe North, we hear how they were able
OL,16,Fto solve it in just three weeks.
